data.text: At our next mandatory meeting this coming Monday, November 19th, we will be hosting guest speaker Dr. Bruce Herman, PhD, who is the director at UCS on campus. He will be speaking on the importance of mental health, so be ready to listen to ask any questions you may have for him! Remember this is a meeting where we will be taking attendance and briefly going over updates before we let Dr. Herman have the floor. We hope to have a great turn-out and see you all there!
